        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَنْ غَشَّ اَلْمُسْلِمِينَ حُشِرَ مَعَ اَلْيَهُودِ يَوْمَ اَلْقِيَامَةِ لِأَنَّهُمْ أَغَشُّ اَلنَّاسِ لِلْمُسْلِمِينَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3987 - Imam (as) said: \"Whoever deceives the Muslims will be resurrected with the Jews on the Day of Judgment, because they are the most deceitful people towards the Muslims.\""
        ]
      }
